<ul><li><cite id="CITEREFJakobsson2008" class="citation journal">Jakobsson, Ármann (2008). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.academia.edu/1348111">"A contest of cosmic fathers: God and giant in Vafþrúðnismál"</a>. <i>Neophilologus</i>. <b>92</b> (2): 263–277. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1007%2Fs11061-007-9056-x">10.1007/s11061-007-9056-x</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Neophilologus&amp;rft.atitle=A+contest+of+cosmic+fathers%3A+God+and+giant+in+Vaf%C3%BEr%C3%BA%C3%B0nism%C3%A1l&amp;rft.volume=92&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=263-277&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1007%2Fs11061-007-9056-x&amp;rft.aulast=Jakobsson&amp;rft.aufirst=%C3%81rmann&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.academia.edu%2F1348111&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVaf%C3%BEr%C3%BA%C3%B0nism%C3%A1l" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></li>
